comments:
The plugin for the applet launcher does not work for OS XP. It can't seem to 
access the zip file. I send a detailed note to Olivier Thomann about a week ago 
from roberthein@rogers.com explaining the problem and also sent a screen shot 
and a copy of the .log file. Also, the help panel does not work either. Points 
to some IP address on the web. Application works great under Win NT 4.0. I'm 
using the build 0508 and the current version of the applet plugin.
I would appreciate if someone to look into this problem. I do development from 
my home pc running XP and I'm stuck when I have to create new applets. 

Thanks,

Robert Hein
